					Desining and implementing a music player integrating machine learning.
				</li>
				<li>
					Using <b>Flutter</b> to create a <b>cross platform</b> basic music player app 
					with two pages songs, and playlists.
				</li>
				<li>
					Using <b>SQLite</b> to store song metadata.
				</li>
